{"tid":1419441,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"假如韓國瑜當選 我地香港都要攪集會聲緩台灣示威","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:25:07.000Z","uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"975f3bafd67d9dd8d11745154cb97866a347c09e","tid":1419441,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:22:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/amparticle/1533476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Famparticle%2F1533476&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=4b80bd38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/amparticle/1533476</a><br />\n<br />\n柯P出黎介票 隨時攪到蔡英文倒輸<br />\n韓國瑜條親共撚屌隨時冷手執個熱煎堆<br />\n本人預計台灣韓國瑜當選後會有年輕人出黎示威！<br />\n<br />\n咁作為唇齒相依既香港<br />\n我地應該要集會以示支持！<br />\n尤其台灣一直都係我地堅實既伙伴！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>台灣一收皮 香港都收皮！ </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然係扯得太遠 但假如我地多人關注埋台灣<br />\n向佢地釋出更多善意 對我地都有幫助！<br />\n<br />\n幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d634aa40937cf11dc13c7e32270f34b704c5dd","tid":1419441,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3b4b7515e4963741d911280baf7f54ac17238fce","tid":1419441,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:25:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}